{"type":"message","id":"bf25e116","parentId":"b0b5df07","timestamp":"2026-06-25T01:00:00.193Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Thursday, June 25th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-25 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1782349200191}}
{"type":"message","id":"49f1b437","parentId":"bf25e116","timestamp":"2026-06-25T01:00:08.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job system event that fires daily at 09:00 Asia/Shanghai. The user is asking me to remember Cursor collaboration rules. The instructions say \"静默确认即可\" (confirm silently), meaning I should just acknowledge without sending any visible reply.\n\nBut wait - this is a cron job delivering a system event, and the instructions say to return summary as plain text. So I should provide a brief confirmation summary.\n\nActually, re-reading: \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" - this says no reply needed, just silently confirm. So I should return a very brief text summary acknowledging the rules refresh."},{"type":"text","text":"已确认记住 Cursor 协作规则。每日规则刷新完成。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782349200192}}
